<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿny qḍy̱ rby ạlḥnwn wdẖạq gẖṣạt ạlmnwn
 mḥrraⁿạ ạ̉sry̱ ạlsjwd rb ạlwry̱ fạdy ạlạ̉nạm
 ạlqrạr- jỷt sẖfạʾ mt fdạʾ fyạlḥbk ạlʿjyb
 lys swạk fbdmạk njwt mn mwt rhyb
